    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235590/extras/c696a0eba712c765d92d48f6fec26579.avif?t=1772446870\" width=1560 height=211 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《大学物语》是一款大学题材的模拟经营恋爱养成游戏，你将扮演一位大一新生，进行四年的大学生活。在这里，你的大学你做主！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235590/extras/59a8212c89c51daacb58122abf4cc6b3.avif?t=1772446870\" width=1560 height=211 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >学习、考试、社交、恋爱、兼职、校园活动……你全都可以体验！甚至你可以种田开网店！！！是默默无闻还是名动校园？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235590/extras/7261b52ec688d682c7e46c0127bbcc75.avif?t=1772446870\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235590/extras/97511c03af2be9f60f26c50d3f4641ac.avif?t=1772446870\" width=1560 height=211 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在大学，你是否会遇到自己生命中的那个她。在这里，你可以了解她们的故事，选择成为他们的蓝颜知己或者另一半，谈一场甜甜的恋爱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235590/extras/0317cf3f4b7e37918a1f938cdb87b839.avif?t=1772446870\" width=1560 height=3006 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235590/extras/b4f3982a7bc1bd01d988b8bec0ca51a1.avif?t=1772446870\" width=1560 height=211 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大学的室友，应该是你大学四年相处时间最长的人。你们一起学习，一起开黑，一起吹牛......他们来自天南海北各省各市，性格迥异，各有特色。在这里，了解他们的故事，体会兄弟间的友情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235590/extras/9999f3f7c3103b07b6bf2ad0164e18ce.avif?t=1772446870\" width=1560 height=3006 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235590/extras/bd13037509c031be62e0cc7dcb5add50.avif?t=1772446870\" width=1560 height=211 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中提供了多条养成路线以及数十种小游戏。体能锻炼、学习考试、才艺培养、竞赛活动、兼职创业……玩家可根据自己的喜好进行对应培养，解锁不同的人生结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235590/extras/b16d3978b31da1e80ea8bad93deeacd6.avif?t=1772446870\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235590/extras/5d22355c87dd1aeb5baa5bacfd3e6e4c.avif?t=1772446870\" width=1560 height=211 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大学四年后，会根据你所选的专业、大学的四年的评分、自身的属性和才艺、是否考研考编、选择的女朋友等条件获得不同的人生结局，总计100+不同人生结局等你解锁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
